 \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like my fish and people are finding worms in the fish.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fish\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"worms\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the fish\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just not good enough.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The standard, we are looking at the best of the best in the world, and we are feeding them not the best.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want people to get better at their roles and jobs and I think that's what the athletes are the best sounding board for.\\\"\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"their roles\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the best sounding board\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was recently reportedthatTeam GBflew in extra chefs from the UK to cook for their athletes, with many boycotting the food on offer in the Olympic village.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999371334027646, \"rank\": 6.285629600579534e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"GBflew\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"extra chefs\", \"fr